<br>
To join a chat room on another server, the format is:<br>
<br>
/join [ServerShortName].[ChatRoomName]<br>
<br>
To send a tell to someone on another server:<br>
<br>
;tell [ServerShortName].[PlayerName] message text<br>
<br>
